this is the contents of my personal ~/  folder on my development machine

It is completley customized for my development preferences:

* Mac OS X
* preferred editor: vim
* Homebrew is installed

If I'm recovering this then do the following:

1) clone this locally to the ~/ folder
2) Move .gitconfig-dist to .gitconfig
3) Copy the following section to .git/info/exclude

.AB64CF89
.CFUserTextEncoding
.Xauthority
.DS_Store
.config
.cups/
.drush/
.dvdcss
.fontconfig
.gem
.gitconfig
